Package: stratigraphr
Type: Package
Title: Archaeological Stratigraphy and Chronological Sequences
Version: 0.2.0
Date: 2018-12-19
Authors@R: person("Joe", "Roe", email = "joe@joeroe.io",
  role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1011-1244"))
Description: A tidy framework for working with archaeological stratigraphy and
    chronology in R. Includes tools for reading, analysing, and visualising
    stratigraphies ("Harris matrices") and sequences as directed graphs; 
    helper functions for using radiocarbon dates in a tidy data analysis; and an
    R interface to OxCal's Chronological Query Language (CQL).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://stratigraphr.joeroe.io, https://github.com/joeroe/stratigraphr
